    <briefdescription>
<para>HAL Mode structure definition. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para><simplesect kind="note"><para>HAL I2C Mode value coding follow below described bitmap :<linebreak/>
 b7 (not used)<linebreak/>
 x : Should be set to 0<linebreak/>
 b6<linebreak/>
 0 : None<linebreak/>
 1 : Memory (HAL I2C communication is in Memory Mode)<linebreak/>
 b5<linebreak/>
 0 : None<linebreak/>
 1 : Slave (HAL I2C communication is in Slave Mode)<linebreak/>
 b4<linebreak/>
 0 : None<linebreak/>
 1 : Master (HAL I2C communication is in Master Mode)<linebreak/>
 b3-b2-b1-b0 (not used)<linebreak/>
 xxxx : Should be set to 0000 </para>
</simplesect>
</para>
    </detaileddescription>
